title: Chest of Drawers (Four)
medium:
Graphite; ruled border in graphite
Support: tracing paper
description:
Four-drawer chest; top drawer, narrower than lower three, overlaps vertical frame of chest; three lower drawers, set within frame, expose frame's edge.  Chest is flush with floor. Two knobs, positioned left and right, per drawer.
Scale: 1"-1'
name: Drawing
